cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Smart Test Picker"
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using these metadata."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Punosevac"
    given-names: "Ljubisa"
    affiliation: "SAP SE"
repository-code: "https://github.com/SAP/smart-test-picker"
abstract: >
  Smart Test Picker is a Gradle and Maven plugin that performs
  regression test selection by mapping per-test runtime coverage
  (collected via JaCoCo) against Git diffs to identify the minimal
  set of tests affected by a code change.
keywords:
  - regression-testing
  - test-selection
  - jacoco
  - gradle-plugin
  - junit5
  - code-coverage
license: Apache-2.0
